  description="Complete Apache Flink guide: true streaming vs micro-batch, DataStream API, event time and watermarks, tumbling/sliding/session windows, stateful processing, Flink SQL, and Flink vs Spark Streaming comparison."
  tool="Apache Flink, stream processing, DataStream, windowing, stateful, event time, Flink SQL"
